(1,'A2','ECOA NOTICE OF ACTION TAKEN_Counter',1,'	<h3>ECOA NOTICE OF ACTION TAKEN</h3>\r\n    <div class=\"centerbt\">Counter Offer With Denial and Statement of Reasons</div>\r\n    <hr/>\r\n    \r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop10\">TO:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.userinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop10\">FROM:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22 lineheight30\">\r\n    	Loan Number:{{$pagedata.loaninfo.loannum}}<br>\r\n        Applicants: {{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}} (Borrower(s)) <br>\r\n		Notice Date:{{$pagedata.loaninfo.notice_date}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>DESCRIPTION OF ACCOUNT, TRANSACTION, OR REQUESTED CREDIT.</h4>\r\n        Application for credit requested by you.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>DESCRIPTION OF ACTION TAKEN.</h4>\r\n        We are unable to offer you credit on the terms that you requested, but can offer you credit on the following terms: A counter offer of ${{$pagedata.loaninfo.loan_amount}}. If this offer is acceptable to you, please notify us on or before {{$pagedata.loaninfo.notice_date_later}} at the address listed above. If you do not accept our offer by this date, then we regret that we are unable to approve your original request.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>PRINCIPAL REASONS FOR ADVERSE ACTION TAKEN.</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.adverse_action}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-25 21:45:08','2017-10-25 21:45:08'),(2,'A2','ECOA NOTICE OF ACTION TAKEN_Counter',2,'<div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>DISCLOSURE OF USE OF INFORMATION OBTAINED FROM AN OUTSIDE SOURCE.</h4>\r\n        Our credit decision was based in whole or in part on information obtained in a credit report from the consumer reporting agency (or agencies) listed below. You have a right under the Fair Credit Reporting Act to know the information contained in your credit file at the consumer reporting agency. The reporting agency played no part in our decision and is unable to supply specific reasons why we have denied credit to you.  You also have a right to a free copy of your report from the reporting agency, if you request it no later than 60 days after you receive this notice. In addition, if you find that any information contained in the report you receive is inaccurate or incomplete, you have the right to dispute the matter with the reporting agency.<br><br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.reporting_agency_list}}<br>\r\n        We also obtained your credit score from the consumer reporting agency {{$pagedata.userinfo.credit_score_source}} and used it in making our credit decision. Your credit score is a number that reflects the information in your consumer report. Your credit score can change, depending on how the information in your consumer report changes.<br>\r\n        <h4>Your credit score: {{$pagedata.userinfo.credit_score}}<br> \r\n        Date: {{$pagedata.userinfo.credit_score_date}}<br>\r\n        Scores range from a low of 500 to a high of 800<br>\r\n        Key factors that adversely affected your credit score:<br> \r\n        {{$pagedata.fico_risk_factor}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	If you have any questions regarding your credit score, you should contact {{$pagedata.userinfo.credit_score_source}} at their address and telephone number above.<br>\r\n		Our credit decision was based in whole or in part on information obtained from an affiliate or from an outside source other than a consumer reporting agency. Under the Fair Credit Reporting Act, you have the right to make a written request, no later than 60 days after you receive this notice, for disclosure of the nature of this information.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>QUESTIONS.</h4>\r\n        If you have any questions regarding this notice, you should contact: <br>\r\n        Creditor\'s Name: {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}<br>\r\n        Creditor\'s Address: {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}<br>\r\n		Creditor\'s Telephone Number:  {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.phonenumber}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n	<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n		{{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-19 06:58:31','2017-10-19 06:58:31'),(3,'A2','ECOA NOTICE OF ACTION TAKEN_Counter',3,'<div class=\"border\">\r\n    	<b>Notice:</b> The federal Equal Credit Opportunity Act prohibits creditors from discriminating against credit applicants on the basis of race, color, religion, national origin, sex, marital status, sexual orientation, military status, age (provided the applicant has the capacity to enter into a binding contract); because all or part of the applicant\'s income derives from any public assistance program; or because the applicant has in good faith exercised any right under the Consumer Credit Protection Act.<br>	\r\n        The federal agency that administers compliance with this law concerning this creditor is:<br>\r\n		<div class=\"marginleft30\">        \r\n            <h4>FDIC</h4>\r\n            1100 Walnut St, Box#11 <br>\r\n            Kansas City, Missouri 64106\r\n		</div>\r\n    </div>\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-19 06:58:21','2017-10-19 06:58:21'),
(5,'B1','CONSUMER CREDIT REPORT NOTICE FOR NEW YORK',1,'<h3>CONSUMER CREDIT REPORT NOTICE FOR NEW YORK</h3>\r\n    <hr/>\r\n    \r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop10\">TO:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.userinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop10\">FROM:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	I understand that you may request and use a consumer report in connection with my application for credit and subsequent consumer reports in connection with any update, renewal or extension of credit. If I ask, you will tell me whether or not you did request a consumer report, and if you did, you will provide me with the name and address of the consumer reporting agency that furnished the report.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<b>SIGNATURES:</b> I acknowledge receipt of a copy of this Consumer Credit Notice for New York on {{$pagedata.loaninfo.note_date}}.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop80 fontsize12\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"width230\"><br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}\r\n    </div>\r\n	\r\n	<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-25 21:51:34','2017-10-25 21:51:34'),
(6,'B2','NOTICE OF NEGATIVE INFORMATION PRESHARING',1,'<h3>NOTICE OF NEGATIVE INFORMATION (PRE-SHARING)</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop22\">LENDER:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    <h4 class=\"margintop10\">BORROWER:</h4>\r\n    <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}</h4>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.userinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.userinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	Federal law requires us to provide the following notice to customers before any \"negative information\" may be furnished to a nationwide consumer reporting agency. \"Negative information\" means information concerning delinquencies, late payments, insolvency, or any form of default. <span class=\"underline\">This notice does not mean that we will be reporting such information about you, only that we may report such information about customers that have not done what they are required to do under our agreement.</span>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	After providing this notice, additional negative information may be submitted without providing another notice.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>We may report information about your account to credit bureaus. Late payments, missed payments, or other defaults on your account may be reflected in your credit report.</h4>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n	<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-20 21:41:15','2017-10-20 21:41:15'),
(7,'B3','NOTICE REGARDING INACCURATE INFORMATION',1,'<h3>NOTICE REGARDING INACCURATE INFORMATION</h3>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	As a participant in the consumer reporting system, we furnish information about our experience with you to consumer reporting agencies. These consumer reports allow us to make credit and other opportunities available to you. If you believe that we have furnished information to a consumer reporting agency that is inaccurate, please notify us at the following address and identify the specific information that is inaccurate.\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	<h4>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</h4>\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}<br>\r\n		{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n    <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n    	{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.phonenumber}}\r\n    </div>\r\n    \r\n	<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    	<hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n         {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2017-10-25 21:45:32','2017-10-25 21:45:32'),
(8,'B4','AUTOMATIC TRANSFER AUTHORIZATION',1,'<h3>AUTOMATIC TRANSFER AUTHORIZATION</h3>\r\n    <hr>\r\n    <div class=\"fontsize12\" >\r\n        <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n            <b>DATE AND PARTIES.</b>  The date of this Automatic Transfer Authorization (Authorization) is {{$pagedata.loaninfo.note_date}}. The parties and their addresses are:\r\n            <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    <h4>ACCOUNT HOLDER:</h4>\r\n                    <h4>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}</h4>\r\n                    {{$pagedata.userinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.userinfo.street2}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.zipcode}}\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    <h4>LENDER:</h4>\r\n                    <h4>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</h4>\r\n                    {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    The pronouns \"you\" or \"your\" refer to the Lender. The pronouns \"I\", \"me\" and \"my\" refer to the Account Holder.\r\n                </div>\r\n             </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n         <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n            <h4>TRANSFER AUTHORIZATION.</h4>\r\n            <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    <b>From Debited Account:Account No.____________________ </b><br>\r\n                    <b>Account Title.</b>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}<br>\r\n                    <b>Account Type.</b> Savings\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    <b>To Credited Account (Loan): Loan/Account No.{{$pagedata.loaninfo.loannum}}</b><br>\r\n                    <b>Loan/Account Title.</b>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}<br>\r\n                    <b>Loan/Account Type.</b> Amortized\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    You will make transfers on the following basis:\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    <b>Amount to be Transferred.</b> ${{$pagedata.loaninfo.first_amount_payment}}<br> \r\n                    <b>Effective Date. </b>{{$pagedata.loaninfo.first_payment_date}}<br>\r\n                    <b>Termination Date.</b> {{$pagedata.loaninfo.manturity_date}}<br>\r\n                    <b>Frequency. </b>{{$pagedata.loaninfo.payment_frequency}}\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n         <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n            <h4>AMENDMENTS AND TERMINATION.</h4>\r\n            <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    I authorize you to charge my Debited Account (Account) for all payments due on the above described Credited Account (Loan). You may continue to charge the Account until the Loan is paid or until I provide you with written notice of cancellation.\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    I understand and agree that if a payment due date falls on a non-business day, the payment amount will be debited from the Account and credited to the Loan as a loan payment on the next day you are open for regular business.\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    I further understand and agree that if the Account does not have a sufficient balance on a day that a payment is to be debited from the Account and credited to the Loan, you may, at your option, suspend further efforts to debit the Account and look to me for the payment and all subsequent payments until such time as all payments under the Loan are current. In no event will availability of any credit line that I may have with you be used in determining whether the Account has a sufficient balance.\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    At your option and sole discretion, you may resume charging the Account without further instruction from me once all payments are current. In the event that you do not resume charging to the Account, you will notify me in writing that this authorization has been cancelled. Such cancellation of this authorization does not excuse me from making timely payment under the terms of the Loan.\r\n                </div>\r\n                <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n                    In any event, you, at your option, may cancel this authorization at any time.\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n         <div class=\"margintop5\">\r\n         <b>SIGNATURES.</b>  By signing, I agree to the terms contained in this Authorization.  I also acknowledge receipt of a copy of this Authorization.\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n         <div class=\"margintop5 marginleft30\">\r\n         ACCOUNT HOLDER:\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n         <div class=\"margintop40 marginleft70\">\r\n         _______________________________________Date_______________<br>\r\n           {{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}\r\n         </div>\r\n         \r\n     </div>\r\n \r\n<div class=\"footer fontsize10\">\r\n    <hr class=\"hr2\">{{$pagedata.footerinfo.curpageinfo}}\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field1}}<br>\r\n        {{$pagedata.footerinfo.field2}}\r\n    </div>','1','2018-05-21 02:46:19','2018-05-21 02:46:19'),
(9,'B5','DISBURSEMENT AUTHORIZATION AND CASH PAYMENT SUMMARY',1,'<h3>DISBURSEMENT AUTHORIZATION AND CASH PAYMENT SUMMARY</h3>\r\n    <hr>\r\n	<div class=\"fontsize12\" >\r\n        <div class=\"margintop10\">\r\n            <b>DATE AND PARTIES.</b> The date of this Disbursement Authorization and Cash Payment Summary is {{$pagedata.loaninfo.note_date}}.  The parties and their addresses are:\r\n            <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n            	<h4 class=\"marginleft30\">LENDER: </h4>\r\n            	<div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n                    <b>{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.name}}</b><br>\r\n                     {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.lenderinfo.street2}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.zipcode}}<br>\r\n                    Telephone: {{$pagedata.lenderinfo.phonenumber}}\r\n                </div>\r\n        	</div>\r\n            <div class=\"margintop10\">\r\n            	<h4 class=\"marginleft30\">BORROWER:</h4>\r\n                <div class=\"marginleft70\">\r\n                    <b>{{$pagedata.userinfo.first_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.middle_name}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.last_name}}</b><br>\r\n                    {{$pagedata.userinfo.street}}{{$pagedata.userinfo.street2}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.city}}, {{$pagedata.userinfo.state}} {{$pagedata.userinfo.zipcode}}\r\n                </div>\r\n            </div>\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"margintop10\">\r\n        	<b>Loan Number:</b>{{$pagedata.loaninfo.loannum}}\r\n        </div>\r\n        \r\n        <div class=\"margintop22\">\r\n        	<b>1.DEFINITIONS.</b> As used in this Disbursement Authorization and Cash Payment Summary, the terms have the following meanings:\r\n            <div class=\"marginleft30\">\r\n            	<b>A.	Pronouns.</b> The pronouns \"I\", \"me\" and \"my\" refer to all Borrowers signing this Disbursement Authorization and Cash Payment Summary, individually and together. \"You\" and 